# Go Formatting Configuration
# 
# This project uses the following Go formatting tools:
# - gofmt: Standard Go formatter
# - goimports: Manages imports and applies gofmt
# - golangci-lint: Comprehensive linter
#
# Usage:
#   Format all Go files: make fmt
#   Check formatting: make fmt-check
#   Run linters: make lint
#
# Configuration:
# - Use tabs for indentation (Go standard)
# - Line length: 120 characters
# - Import grouping: stdlib, external, internal
# - Function comments above function declarations 